text.tspan: Millennium Development Goal (MDG) 4.A was to reduce global child mortality (children under 5 years old) rates by
two-thirds from 1990 to 2015. The global target was therefore a reduction to 30 deaths per 1,000 live births by 2015.

text.textPath: Global target: reduce child mortality by two-thirds (to 30 per 1,000)
